{"tid":1373272,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"（公民學習故事-初階）《小豬問為什麼要有選舉選出村長？》","createTime":"2019-07-27T15:03:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T18:14:42.000Z","uid":64232,"like":47,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"9b1582fd9b44e4bfe9343faf635b7f0c43fde593","tid":1373272,"uid":64232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:03:32.000Z","msg":"從前有兩條村。"},{"pid":"85b73c55282c3ffd5a47301fd0049583018f724c","tid":1373272,"uid":64232,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:03:40.000Z","msg":"一條是皇帝村，村長是黑豬，終身制，任何事都由他一隻豬決定，所以做任何事都雷風厲行，發展迅速。"},{"pid":"e55a07396918005e1188d2a3798c899b971e67bd","tid":1373272,"uid":64232,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:03:51.000Z","msg":"一條是選舉村，村長不定，每幾年就由村民選舉一次，做任何決定都要諮詢村民的意見，所以發展比鄰村慢。"},{"pid":"a35e407ebfa914eb7846f077156f5cd7a7f6b329","tid":1373272,"uid":64232,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:04:01.000Z","msg":"住在民主村的小豬問媽媽，為什麼要有選舉呢？是因為活在選舉村會開心一點嗎？"},{"pid":"2a6fdf6220c41fdc34361491f8bae4d4146b1a32","tid":1373272,"uid":64232,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:04:11.000Z","msg":"小豬媽媽說：「這個不一定，皇帝村的村民可能會快樂一點。」"},{"pid":"fca42ffec478abd0bd1fe76c71dfc5c5518965ea","tid":1373272,"uid":64232,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:04:22.000Z","msg":"「那為什麼要有選舉，又慢又煩人。」"},{"pid":"04120bc5fafebc8fd7d9280ceebcbd833979356c","tid":1373272,"uid":64232,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:04:33.000Z","msg":"「是呀，選舉有許多缺點，但我們要選舉是因為怕『萬一』。」"},{"pid":"5745acf9315cfdbbc629e82bb74fb8f8a8c03a27","tid":1373272,"uid":64232,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:04:43.000Z","msg":"「什麼是『萬一』。」"},{"pid":"6f3b8f99f74831ed2e6a8e2075c3f76815695f0d","tid":1373272,"uid":64232,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:05:00.000Z","msg":"「皇帝村的村民可以生活得很好，但萬一村長想幹壞事，把村民們心愛的小豬BB煮熟當成火腿賣出去，或是用棍打死豬們，村民也沒有能力阻止。即使壞事做盡後，黑豬還是高高在上的村長。<br />\n<br />\n但民主的選舉下，我們就能趕這個壞村長下台了，雖然未必能保證下一個上台的是好豬，但起碼有選擇的權力。所以我們為了心愛的你們、下一代著想，防止你們被賣出去，自然要選舉啦。」"},{"pid":"146bcedf7dc8270a452077bc6e3e0ad0b44a9c08","tid":1373272,"uid":64232,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:05:46.000Z","msg":"For身邊嘅「BB仔」學公民概念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ae65e100cff5dc4b78f623b3664bc8ab587a774","tid":1373272,"uid":196252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:07:42.000Z","msg":"我愛Gay廉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51db49720c1bdd5e5800a8f6c36fc7df3fe13683","tid":1373272,"uid":220057,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:08:33.000Z","msg":"兒童故事，唔錯。"},{"pid":"49d9c6b6f3f5e368f4c07cc7406e5d44e101ddcb","tid":1373272,"uid":37713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:09:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2571b0fce6ab992405c60c1f8c02aa097f15460e","tid":1373272,"uid":126561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:09:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5819f749057121d47bf1a4c5d13fdf0b18dcce4b","tid":1373272,"uid":263659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51db49720c1bdd5e5800a8f6c36fc7df3fe13683","tid":1373272,"uid":220057,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:08:33.000Z","msg":"兒童故事，唔錯。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:13:24.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似童謠咁，隨時可以輸出革命添"},{"pid":"950e42ba4130e6400d46bfb591103d50d126aec2","tid":1373272,"uid":171633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51db49720c1bdd5e5800a8f6c36fc7df3fe13683","tid":1373272,"uid":220057,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:08:33.000Z","msg":"兒童故事，唔錯。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:17:37.000Z","msg":"攞黎話俾小朋友知 提高公民意識係好事"},{"pid":"3dd89b368ef5de38df84a5523de99afcaf0320ef","tid":1373272,"uid":64232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51db49720c1bdd5e5800a8f6c36fc7df3fe13683","tid":1373272,"uid":220057,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:08:33.000Z","msg":"兒童故事，唔錯。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:48:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"830edc3e8e688e9361c092fcad71c1c013698f54","tid":1373272,"uid":46814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:31:12.000Z","msg":"多謝你，喺呢個困局入面依然能夠安慰大家嘅無助無力"},{"pid":"3d4576ba87df7dd05a1fe42b56b03a1781ac149d","tid":1373272,"uid":8820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T17:50:55.000Z","msg":"高汁要推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08f3ea55e50e984de70ed86cc5625c4706c451ef","tid":1373272,"uid":188546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T18:42:02.000Z","msg":"好鍾意睇你嘅文"},{"pid":"a984cb8ae9abacdea78d9142cf93c594137c3012","tid":1373272,"uid":28818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:25:00.000Z","msg":"我愛Gay廉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a3afd36762cabe97af2dee1612de30227a57f76","tid":1373272,"uid